<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
        <h2>Password Reset</h2>
        <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
        <p>We have received your request to reset your password. Please use the following OTP code to reset your
            password:</p>
        <p><strong>OTP Code: {{otpCode}}</strong></p>
        <p>Please use this code to reset your password by following the instructions on our app.</p>
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
        <p>Thank you,</p>
        <p>Aquavita</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>